---
title: Cal Smart Fiery Salmon with Asian-Style Coleslaw and Cilantro Rice
description: For a calorie-smart meal with sass, look no further! Succulent salmon is topped with a fiery ginger sauce, then served with crunchy red cabbage and edamame slaw for the perfect spicy, savoury bite.
